[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1110","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1110.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1452","title":"Microsoft Windows NT GINA 权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的 GINA（图形化标识与身份验证）组件存在权限许可和访问控制漏洞。具有物理访问权限的攻击者可在目标系统已锁定工作站的情况下，通过将剪贴板内容粘贴（CTRL-V）到用户名输入框中，从而泄露锁定用户剪贴板中的敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者需具备物理接触条件，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1452"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.233","remediation":"升级到 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统，这些版本已修复 GINA 在锁定状态下允许粘贴剪贴板内容的问题。如无法升级，可通过组策略禁用交互式登录前的粘贴功能，或确保物理访问环境受控，仅允许授权人员接触终端。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91788829326419&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91764169410814&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91822011021558&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q214/8/02.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/198","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1975"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1110.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1107","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1107.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1451","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server 和 Site Server 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"IIS 4.0 及 Site Server 3.0 自带的 Winmsdp.exe 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过构造特制 HTTP 请求，利用该示例文件读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 平台上的 IIS 4.0 和 Site Server 3.0 版本，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1451"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.107","remediation":"删除 IIS 4.0 或 Site Server 3.0 服务器上的 Winmsdp.exe 示例文件（默认位于 /Msadc/Samples/Selector/ 目录），或升级到 IIS 5.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中禁用该示例目录的脚本执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q231/3/68.asp","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3271"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1107.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1105","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1105.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1444","title":"Alibaba genkey 交易明文发送漏洞","description":"Alibaba 2.0 的 genkey 密钥生成工具在生成 RSA 密钥对时错误地将私钥指数设置为 1，导致对应的公钥指数也为 1，使得 SSL 会话密钥以明文形式传输。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过网络嗅探窃取加密通信内容，或实施中间人攻击篡改数据。该漏洞影响 Alibaba 2.0 版本，且 Netscape Navigator 和 Internet Explorer 浏览器均不会对使用此类无效证书的 SSL 站点发出安全警告，进一步扩大了风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1444"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:27.233","remediation":"立即停止使用 Alibaba 2.0 的 genkey 工具生成密钥对，改用 OpenSSL 等标准工具生成 RSA 密钥（指数 e 至少为 65537）。如系统仍运行 Alibaba 2.0，应升级到支持安全密钥生成的版本或迁移至其他支持 TLS 加密的电子商务平台，避免交易数据以明文传输。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://catless.ncl.ac.uk/Risks/20.41.html#subj4","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1444.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1444","https://github.com/C2SP/wycheproof/blob/fc24cd5b787d8e496bff31b0468af693a652b0f2/doc/bib.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1444.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1444.json","https://github.com/huahua132/skynet_fly/blob/8d09dfdbf29612dbcc6b3acdcbede80434add9ef/3rd/openssl/wycheproof/doc/rsa.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-frc4-j6xj-vg8w/GHSA-frc4-j6xj-vg8w.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1444.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001044.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--600b6cd9-97c9-4150-9f4a-b4a83d5d1e48.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1105.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1094","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1094.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1382","title":"Novell NetWare NFS 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"NetWare NFS 模式 1 和 2 在实现 Unix \"只读\" 标志时存在权限许可漏洞。该漏洞源于系统将设置为 \"只读\" 的文件所有权更改为 root 用户，导致本地攻击者可通过创建 setuid 程序并将其标记为 \"只读\" 来利用此机制，NetWare-NFS 会自动将其转换为 root 所有的 setuid 程序，从而使攻击者获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Unix 平台上的 NetWare NFS 服务，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1382"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:19.213","remediation":"立即安装 Novell 官方补丁（TID 2940551），或升级 NetWare NFS 至不受影响的版本。如无法升级，应禁止普通用户在 NFS 共享目录中创建 setuid 文件，可在 exports 配置中添加 `nosuid` 挂载选项作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88427711321769&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90295697702474&w=2","http://support.novell.com/cgi-bin/search/tidfinder.cgi?2940551","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7246.php"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1094.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1080","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1080.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1364","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 系统内核中存在本地拒绝服务漏洞，当本地用户通过 GetThreadContext 或 SetThreadContext 函数传入非法的内核模式地址时，系统未对输入指针进行有效验证，导致内核崩溃引发蓝屏。攻击者需具备本地登录权限且能够执行恶意程序方可利用，无法远程触发。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 所有版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1364"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.977","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 5 (SP5) 或更高版本（推荐 SP6a）即可修复此漏洞。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议迁移至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）。临时缓解措施：限制本地用户登录权限，仅允许受信任用户进行交互式登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q142/6/53.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7421.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1364.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1364","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1364.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1364.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h9g2-x4rf-46v3/GHSA-h9g2-x4rf-46v3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84476/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1364.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/4a6e09a063689f2d97734100478c1eef6f6dc387/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1080.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1079","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1079.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1363","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 3.51 及 4.0 系统中存在本地拒绝服务漏洞。本地用户可通过运行程序对同一文件创建大量锁，导致系统非分页池（NonPagedPool）资源耗尽，从而触发系统崩溃。该漏洞攻击前提为拥有本地登录权限，无法远程利用，影响范围限于 Windows NT 系列版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1363"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.840","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本系统（如 Windows 2000/XP），此漏洞在后续版本中已修复。对于无法升级的系统，可通过组策略限制非授信用户的本地交互式登录权限，降低攻击面。在注册表 `HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Session Manager\\Memory Management` 中调整 `NonPagedPoolSize` 值可缓解资源耗尽风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q163/1/43.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7405.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1363.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1363","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1363.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1363.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r2f7-pcrq-mgm9/GHSA-r2f7-pcrq-mgm9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84483/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1363.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-410.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1079.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1078","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1078.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1362","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Win32k.sys 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 SP2 之前版本的 Win32k.sys 内核模块中存在参数校验缺陷，本地用户通过向特定 WIN32K 函数传递异常参数触发该漏洞，可导致系统内核崩溃引发拒绝服务。由于该漏洞需要本地访问权限且仅为 DoS 影响，危害等级较低。Microsoft 在 Windows NT 4.0 SP2 中修复了此问题。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1362"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.720","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 2 (SP2) 或更高版本，该补丁修复了 Win32k.sys 对畸形参数的处理缺陷。如无法升级，可通过限制本地用户对系统的交互式登录权限降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q160/6/01.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7403.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1362.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1362","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1362.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1362.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9j5c-5cw9-cqxv/GHSA-9j5c-5cw9-cqxv.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1362.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001038.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ac2f0f86-48c5-460b-a85e-14c08f2e58bf.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1078.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1077","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1077.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1360","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 内核句柄处理本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 存在内核句柄处理缺陷，本地用户可通过用户态应用程序关闭已在内核态打开的文件句柄，当内核尝试关闭该句柄时由于双重释放导致系统崩溃，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者需拥有本地登录权限才能利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1360"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.473","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a (SP6a) 或更高版本，该版本修复了内核模式句柄在用户态关闭导致系统崩溃的问题。如无法升级，限制非授权用户本地登录系统作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q160/6/50.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7402.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1360.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1360","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1360.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1360.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-77p5-wxj2-c3mh/GHSA-77p5-wxj2-c3mh.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84461/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1360.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/4a6e09a063689f2d97734100478c1eef6f6dc387/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1077.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1076","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1076.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1359","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Ntconfig.pol 策略安全绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 存在安全策略绕过漏洞。当服务器主机名超过 13 个字符时，系统无法正确解析 Ntconfig.pol 文件中的全局组策略配置，导致已设限制策略无法生效。攻击者利用该漏洞可绕过管理员设定的安全策略获取非授权访问权限，影响 Windows NT 系列系统。此漏洞源于系统在处理长主机名时策略引擎的异常行为，无需特殊工具即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1359"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.343","remediation":"将服务器主机名缩短至 13 个字符以内，确保 Ntconfig.pol 全局组策略正常生效。安装微软 KB Q163875 提供的 hotfix 补丁以彻底修复该问题。鉴于 Windows NT 已停止安全支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q163/8/75.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7401.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1359.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1359","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1359.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1359.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7hww-85g7-g9hc/GHSA-7hww-85g7-g9hc.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87900/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1359.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/4a6e09a063689f2d97734100478c1eef6f6dc387/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1076.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1075","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1075.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1358","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 本地策略绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 系统中，当管理员修改用户策略时，若本地 ntconfig.pol 文件对用户不可写入，策略无法正确更新，导致本地用户可通过将该策略文件设为只读等方式绕过系统强制执行的访问限制。该漏洞允许低权限用户在未授权情况下提升操作权限，危害系统安全策略的完整性。攻击者需要具有本地登录权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1358"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.220","remediation":"确保 ntconfig.pol 文件的 NTFS 权限正确配置，仅允许 Administrators 完全控制，禁止普通用户具有写入权限。建议升级到 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本，后续版本的策略应用机制已修复此问题。如无法升级，可定期检查 ntconfig.pol 文件权限完整性并启用审计策略监控异常权限变更。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q157/6/73.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7400.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1358.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1358","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1358.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1358.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m4fw-6g2w-g44w/GHSA-m4fw-6g2w-g44w.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84433/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1358.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001035.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1075.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1072","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1072.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1355","title":"Compaq Management Agents for Servers 弱配置默认口令漏洞","description":"Compaq Insight Management Agent 4.23及之前版本、Management Agents for Servers 4.40及之前版本在安装BMC Patrol组件时，会自动创建一个名为PFCUser的默认账户，该账户使用固定默认密码且拥有过高系统权限。远程攻击者可利用此默认凭证登录目标系统，获取未授权访问权限，进而执行恶意操作。该漏洞影响大量Compaq/HP服务器管理系统，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1355"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.847","remediation":"升级 Compaq Insight Management Agent 至 4.23 以上版本，或 Management Agents for Servers 至 4.40 以上版本；同时删除或禁用默认创建的 PFCUser 账户，并修改所有相关账户的默认口令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93542118727732&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93654336516711&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93759822430801&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94183795025294&w=2","http://www.compaq.com/products/servers/management/advisory.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3231","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1355.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1355","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1355.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1355.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qmhx-84gq-mqf3/GHSA-qmhx-84gq-mqf3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87874/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1355.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--203e8cbd-6b3c-4878-8673-6db7c739ac0c.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/SecurityTapestry-Queen/nvd-cve-api-search/blob/6901bdceb94c779e36bd5f694ddd48cafcd5c8d3/archive/2025-04-06/report-04-06-2025-20-58-46.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1072.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1055","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1055.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1339","title":"Linux 和 FreeBSD NAT 记录路由请求拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux 2.2.10 及更早版本（使用 ipchains）以及 FreeBSD 3.2（使用 ipfw）的网络地址转换（NAT）功能存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 ping -R（记录路由）ICMP 数据包，触发内核在处理路由记录选项时出现异常，导致系统内核崩溃（kernel panic）。该漏洞攻击条件简单，无需认证即可远程触发，影响运行上述版本 Linux 及 FreeBSD 操作系统的网络设备。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1339"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.823","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.11 及以上版本，或升级 FreeBSD 至 3.3 及以上版本。对于仍运行此类老旧系统的环境，建议迁移至受支持的现代版本（如 Linux 6.x 或 FreeBSD 13.x），并在防火墙层面过滤 ICMP 带记录路由选项（record route）的数据包作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93277426802802&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93277766505061&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7257.php","http://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v2.2/patch-2.2.11.gz","http://www.osvdb.org/6105","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1339.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1339","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1339.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1339.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8m8f-vqxq-q9r6/GHSA-8m8f-vqxq-q9r6.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87884/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4321c2f2-9dc5-429a-bd37-0385455013c1.json","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1339.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1055.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1051","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1051.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1335","title":"Red Hat Linux cmu-snmp snmpd 配置错误漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 4.0 系统中 cmu-snmp 软件包 3.3-1 之前版本的 snmpd 服务器存在配置错误漏洞。由于默认配置不当，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞对目标系统上的敏感信息进行读取或写入操作，导致信息泄露或系统配置被篡改。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 4.0 及使用相关 cmu-snmp 组件的系统，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1335"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.290","remediation":"升级 cmu-snmp 软件包至 3.3-1 或更高版本，并修改 SNMP 配置文件 /etc/snmp/snmpd.conf，将默认 public/private 团体字改为复杂随机字符串；同时在 iptables 防火墙中限制仅信任 IP 可访问 UDP 161 端口，禁用 SNMP 写权限（read-only）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh40-errata-general.html#cmu-snmp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7251","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1