T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88609666024181&w=2","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#elm","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1334.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1334","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1334.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9pwm-wh34-fpxm/GHSA-9pwm-wh34-fpxm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001031.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1334.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1050.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1047","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1047.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1331","title":"Red Hat Linux netcfg 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 4.2 中的 netcfg 2.16-1 网络配置工具存在安全配置缺陷，当特定选项被设置后，系统重启时以太网接口的控制权会被不当授予普通用户。本地攻击者可利用此漏洞在未授权的情况下关闭网络接口，导致目标系统失去网络连接能力，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 4.2 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，攻击前提是攻击者拥有本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1331"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:12.733","remediation":"升级 netcfg 至修复版本，或应用 Red Hat RH42 errata 中针对 netcfg 的安全更新。该漏洞在 Red Hat Linux 4.2 的 netcfg 2.16-1 中存在，建议禁用 netcfg 的自动接口控制选项作为临时缓解。对于已停止支持的旧版本，建议迁移至现代受支持的 RHEL 发行版（如 RHEL 7/8/9），并确保网络管理组件保持最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7245.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh42-errata-general.html#netcfg","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1331.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1331","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1331.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1331.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qcqp-mmmc-3pj9/GHSA-qcqp-mmmc-3pj9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84435/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1331.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ad7c142ce47bdca962dc5352eae3764ce44639d2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1047.toml"}]